com.rohanclan.cfml.parser.xpath
Class XPathSearch

java.lang.Object
  com.rohanclan.cfml.parser.xpath.XPathSearch
public class XPathSearch
extends java.lang.Object

Supply a basic search string (i.e. a single node name). Currently supported are the following syntaxes: "aTagName", "//aTagName" Please note that this WILL be changing sooner or later. If it does change it will be completely different.

Author:
Oliver Tupman
